#### **Phase 3: Clean CTASection.vue (10 min)**

**Before:**
```vue
<style scoped>
@keyframes float { ... }         /* ~60 lines of   */
@keyframes float-reverse { ... } /* duplicated     */
@keyframes float-slow { ... }    /* keyframes      */

